<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
<head>
    <title>Index</title>
    <script src="@Url.Content("/Scripts/jquery-3.4.1.min.js")" type="text/javascript">
    </script>

    <script src="@Url.Content("/Scripts/jquery-ui-1.9.0.min.js")"></script>

    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(function () {

            $("#Button1").click(
                function () {
                    $(".TheBox").animate({ fontSize: '20px', BorderWidth: '5px', backgroundColor: '#006600', color: 'yellow', left: '+=30px', borderColor: '#0000E6', borderWidth: '8px', width: '+=100px' }, 500);
                });
        });
    </script>

    <style type="text/css">
        .TheBox {
            border-width: 3px;
            border-color: Red;
            border-style: solid;
            position: relative;
            width: 500px;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Candara;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="TheBox">
        <h3>ASP.NET MVC</h3>
        <div>The ASP.NET MVC Framework is a web application framework that implements the model-view-controller (MVC) pattern.</div>
    </div>
    <br />

    <div class="TheBox">
        <h3>HTML 5</h3>
        <div>HTML5 is a markup language for structuring and presenting content for the World Wide Web and a core technology of the Internet.</div>
    </div>
    <input id="Button1" type="button" value="Animate" />

</body>
</html>

